{
  "stem": "6076.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The only thing I will tell him, he should lie with his age.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He should say he's 16 instead of 14 or 13, you know, to make himself older.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But he didn't look like 16.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "A 16-year-old boy, you could recognize.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But he looked like a-- he look like a boychick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he told him what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And because you have two sisters here, they will take care of you, to wash your shirt, or to be after you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you want to work together with your sisters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And maybe you have a chance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's the only thing what we can tell him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I thanked him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He told my brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I-- they let me in to see him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was tied in with a chain near his chair in the jail.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My heart bleeded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I told him, look, Shmulek, you have to say that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You have to remember your date that you are 16 and birthday.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Otherwise they wouldn't believe you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so they came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they looked at him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they told him, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's a small boy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But by luck, by luck, they say, you want to work?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Where do you want to work?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I want to work with my sisters.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they, they gave him to work to my machine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So that was, that was the incident with my brother Shmulek.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That, that's the way he survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So that's how Shmulek, and you, and Tobcha stayed together?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, in camp.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Until-- we stayed in the camp, all three of us together, until 1944.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was on November-- month of November.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Didn't I give you the date, the date of what month?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think it was in June.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I really don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I know it was the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
